title: Photos I have clicked in the last week are missing from my phone and from google photos app
content:
Last week (from 14 to 16 January 2020) I have taken several photos and videos, which I am able to access till 17th January 2020. And due to warning of insufficient space of my phone, I have tried to back up these photos & videos on cellular data. 

In this process I have observed that all the photos of the above said dates are lost. Please help me out what I can do to retrieve this photos and videos.
